      "id": "f1241eab-7664-4605-a768-e42b86a6a73c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Paper presents end to end model that makes feature extraction from multi souce behavioral data to predict performance. Approach combines LSTM and CNN and tests with data from the University of Beijing show that the DL model outperforms multiple ML conventional ML models.",
